\usepackage{upgreek}
\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
$$ - D\left. {\frac{{\partial C}} {{\partial n}}} \right|_{{\text{wall}}} = KC_{\text{w}} $$\end{document} where the oxygen diffusivity was 1 × 10−5cm2/s1.
